  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Trial to evaluate efficacy and safety of nitazoxanide in the treatment of colds due to
      Enterovirus/Rhinovirus infection
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Multicenter, randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled trial to evaluate efficacy and
      safety of nitazoxanide in the treatment of colds due to Enterovirus/Rhinovirus infection
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
